        "mimage": "shopify://shop_images/Group_2_800x_png.png",
        "details": "<p> <b class=\"value-bold\"> Moth Magic <b></b> </b></p> Inspired by a head clearing, invigorating walk in the\ncrisp mountain air, this delightfully clean and minty\nblend offers an uplifting, energising and super cool\naroma.",
        "heading-position": false
      }
    },
    "image_with_text_2_bjM3r6": {
