        "mimage": "shopify://shop_images/Group_1_800x_png.png",
        "details": "<p> <b class=\"value-bold\"> Zingy Spring</b> </p> A spray of this exclusive scent will transport you to a fresh Mediterranean kitchen, with notes of lush greens, sweet, woody marjoram and vibrant lemon, it’s the perfect welcome to Spring.",
